  p Great news! Your Priest Account on BookMyGuruji has been approved. 🎉🙏
  p You are now verified and your profile is live and available for users to book your services.
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}/dashboard`, target='_blank') Go to your Dashboard
  p Make sure to keep your availability up to date so devotees can schedule ceremonies with you.
  p If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.
  p - The BookMyGuruji Team
